title: HG Fortune Plugin Collection - Uranium Willy
description:
My collection of the sadly too obscure VST company HG Fortune's line of incredible VSTi plugins. These are all great and each comes with loads of presets. Drumburst and Precumat are great drum machines. These sounds are well suited for the soundscape crowd, or for people making music for games. Hard to describe in words really. If you love freaky and atmospheric sounds this package is for you. This is what is included and there a few more things as well, different versions  of a couple instruments, but I think all full versions are included. I put this together over time and they all work, just drop the .dll file (all 32 bit) into your default VST folder and your off. I think all have PDF manuals. No Passwords or cracks needed. 
 
You can check out what these plugins in look like here: www.hgf-synthesizer.com

Simply mind boggling is all I can say.
